When you attune to this ring you sense an itch to take action.

While worn this shiny pinky ring grants +3 bonus to your [rules]Initiative[/rules] rolls. It often tingles when you are about to go first.

You may cast [spells]Longstrider[/spells] on yourself with a [action]Magic[/action] action 1/day using this ring.

When another magic item grants a greater bonus to Initiative this ring may still be used to cast spells.

Crafting this ring requires a bit of [monster]Sahuagin[/monster] or [monster]Stirge[/monster].
